    <div class="markdown level0 summary"><p>Linearly interpolates between two values.</p>
</div>
    <div class="markdown level0 conceptual"></div>
    
      
        <div class="codewrapper">
          <pre><code class="lang-csharp hljs">public static float Lerp(float value1, float value2, float amount)</code></pre>
