    <h id="Microsoft_Xna_Framework_MathHelper_Lerp_System_Single_System_Single_System_Single__remarks">Remarks</h>
    <div class="markdown level0 remarks"><p>This method performs the linear interpolation based on the following formula:</p>
<pre><code>value1 + (value2 - value1) * amount</code></pre>.
<p>Passing amount a value of 0 will cause value1 to be returned, a value of 1 will cause value2 to be returned.
See <a class="xref" href="Microsoft.Xna.Framework.MathHelper.LerpPrecise.html#Microsoft_Xna_Framework_MathHelper_LerpPrecise_System_Single_System_Single_System_Single_">LerpPrecise(Single, Single, Single)</a> for a less efficient version with more precision around edge cases.</p>
</div>
    
    
    
    

